The paper deals with compressed sensing, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also presents a video compression scheme, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper discusses the use of a permutation to reduce the required order of restricted isometry property condition, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.SI).
